INSERT INTO `information_post` VALUES (4, 103, 1, 9, '发现儿子到生理期了怎么办？', 'http://gl.sxwlwq.cn/0ffc083d38b74967a06d58141075ff27_1618911372883.png', 1, 'top', '<p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">发现儿子到了生理期，最好的办法就是交给父母处理，父母最懂孩子。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">儿子发育比较早，12岁就出现了第一次遗精的现象，发现他遗精，也是出于一个偶然的机会。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">为了培养孩子的自律能力，儿子从6岁开始，就一个人睡在他的房间里面。那天早晨我叫他起床的时候，他并没有什么动静，反而显得有些不耐烦，好像是发生了什么事，我就快点催促他起床，因为今天还要上学。</p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/tos-cn-i-0022/0ffc083d38b74967a06d58141075ff27\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline; margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></div><p class=\"syl-page-br\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; height: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">他于是就赶忙起床，把我从门外面拉去吃饭，不让我进他的房间，我想想也没什么，就和他一起吃饭，让他赶快吃完饭去上学。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">吃完饭之后，就急匆匆地跑去上学了，而我在给他收拾房间的时候，却发现他的床单上面却有些潮湿的感觉。我以为是他尿床了，伸手去摸，发现有一块地方都是潮乎乎的，摸上去还有一点发粘，我又闻了闻，发现不是尿，后来趁着老公还没有去上班，把他叫过来，让他看了看。</p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/tos-cn-i-0022/baccef5bbe1a410ea000340a5d60e907\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline; margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></div><p class=\"syl-page-br\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; height: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">老公，看到此情景也有些尴尬，一时间不知道该说些。我问老公，这到底是怎么回事？老公说：“孩子长大了。”我很无奈，长大了，我就得洗床单吗？回来得好好教训他一番。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">老公没听我说几句就赶忙上班去了，留我一个人在家里收拾房间。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">孩子中午回来的时候，我看他眼神躲躲闪闪的，猜他肯定知道昨晚发生了什么事。由于中午时间比较紧促，我也就没有问他，毕竟明天就是周六、周日了，等有时间再问他。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">孩子晚上回来的时候，我跟孩子说：“床单什么都给你换了，以后要注意点。”孩子瞬间脸就红了下来，赶忙躲进了房间，晚饭都没吃，怎么叫都不开门。</p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/tos-cn-i-0022/4cce282a7cb74e54a6ddbf89be78b7ca\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline; margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></div><p class=\"syl-page-br\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; height: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">我跟老公说，我是不是说错什么话了？老公说不用管他，让他冷静冷静，自己就清楚了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">我对老公的表现也很无奈，对自己的孩子都不能上点心吗？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">晚上的时候我就跟老公说，这都是你们男人之间的事，你们男人之间自己解决吧，我一个女人也不在里边掺和了。后来我就把这件事全权交给老公了。</p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/tos-cn-i-0022/f10a219b9f35483cb936b670b5286847\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline; margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></div><p class=\"syl-page-br\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; height: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">第二天早上为了避免尴尬，我就和姐妹出去逛街去了，留老公一个人在家里。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">据老公所言，等我走之后，孩子自己就把门打开了，然后和老公一起吃饭，一起聊天，然后就说了说昨天早上发生的那件事儿。老公给孩子科普了一些这方面的知识，还说这都是不是什么大事儿，只要注意好个人卫生就行了，对于这件事没有必要担心，毕竟这是每个男人都必须要经历的事。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">孩子对老公的话也是蛮上心的，他说他自己在网络上也了解这方面的知识。但就是我妈问起来就是特的难受和尴尬，不想让她知道。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">后来老公把这些话给了我说，我也挺同意孩子看法的。毕竟孩子都已经长大了，没有必要什么事都知道，什么事都了解，孩子也需要有一些自己的私人空间，对此，我也是能够理解的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">男孩子和女孩子一样，每个月都会有那么几天生理期。而男生的生理期则是水满则溢的原理，有时是内部的，有时是外力的作用产生，不管是哪一种，都要做到自爱节制，不伤身体，及时清理私处和内裤。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">后来我想想把这件事交给他父亲一个人做也是不对的，作为母亲，应该给孩子更多的关爱和帮助，让他了解母爱也是伟大的。</span></p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/tos-cn-i-0022/de23d846a36742e4865428df8f1910a8\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline; margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></div><p class=\"syl-page-br\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; height: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><u style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">结语。</u></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">我想说的是，发现男孩儿到了生理期，作为母亲的千万不要担忧，也不要过于忧虑，毕竟那是孩子成长的一个过程，我们应该高兴才对，这也标志着孩子长大了。而且关于这个问题，父母不要过多的多加干涉，父母在一起共同引导孩子，才能做出一个良好的榜样。光靠父亲是不行的，光靠母亲也是不行的，就父母共同对待这个问题，才能有一个更好的结果。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: justify;\">大家对于自己的孩子到了生理期，这个问题是怎么看待的呢？一起来分享一下吧！</p>', '', 100, 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, '2021-04-20 17:36:26', '2021-04-20 17:36:51');
